Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Reduces the endurance cost of a power by {Boost.Attrib.Endurance.Scale}% and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}%.  This enhancement can only be slotted by Controllers and may be slotted into most control powers.
DisplayName: Attuned Will of the Controller C
